Package: wbdataset
Title: Making Datasets Truly Interoperable and Reusable in R with Wikibase
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Antal", , "daniel.antal@dataobservatory.eu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1689-0557"))
Description: Create tidy datasets from Wikidata or a Wikibase instance and add them
   to a tidy R dataset object, or prepare R native datasets in a way that they can be added to 
   a Wikibase semantic database.
